      <title>由于汽车行业陷入困境，大众汽车销量放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/volkswagen-sees-revenue-growth-slowing-as-industry-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车公司表示，随着汽车行业应对电动汽车需求下滑和竞争加剧，今年销量增长将放缓，该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/volkswagen-sees-revenue-growth-slowing-as-industry-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 14:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
